OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPartly cloud
OL,6,Fthis evening with a few showers. Then
OL,7,Fthe rest of the night will see
OL,8,Fvariable amounts of cloud and
OL,9,Foccasional showers. A cold night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FAfter a mainly dry start with
OL,12,Fthe odd shower, rain spreads
OL,13,Fsoutheastwards shortly before midday,
OL,14,Fclearing from the north through the
OL,15,Fafternoon. Becoming breezy for a time
OL,16,Fin the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
