OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCold
OL,6,Fand mainly dry on Monday, a few light
OL,7,Fwintry showers. Early rain on Tuesday
OL,8,Fclearing to showers. Further showers
OL,9,Fon Wednesday.
